{"tid":2517253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟呢d專門笑鳩黃絲既page有幾多？","createTime":"2021-05-05T08:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T11:22:07.000Z","uid":9747,"like":99,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"bee023732b27ee53ddb86c58fed7da6eceaaf693","tid":2517253,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"page名寫就寫著社運，但狙擊黃絲分分鐘仲勁過藍絲page<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最叻將所有問題講成係香港人既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢單野又無啦啦係防疫撚既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmboFiNsUfnSfdGPpk76WE8C7v1cXYiJt2J9nUJLrCVVVy?filename=pS7eM9g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpS7eM9g.png&h=04c6e2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時扮都廢事扮，直接就笑鳩同路人<br />\n通常反駁就話無當過人係同路人，話人泛粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRUNcDJ7srhpsjaLv4qgwj9dxev5gBfHdGjR8mXtpNt2x?filename=xy9g0ui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxy9g0ui.png&h=217857c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者直接就笑鳩黃屍，同藍屍無異<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXoWfGBqi6XhCPYiiDyreDsKyhViCur8dk3zNeZjGB6N7?filename=J239A2F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ239A2F.png&h=72551705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有個共通點就係佢哋永遠都只係佢自己page屌連登仔<br />\n比連登屌到唔敢出聲就係自己page圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者幫其他同類page護航<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdLcD9apsoXSYDZSiunCN61sGCs2kN3UuEYY2ZLeeovpR?filename=CvHuA2H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvHuA2H.png&h=3d37af98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上只係求其碌2野，頭十個post有大部份都係笑香港人為主<br />\n<br />\n呢d熱狗五毛衛星page多數內容都係差唔多<br />\n而且follower唔多<br />\n但page數量就多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍屍page都無佢地咁活躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e7cdbde785607c11e06d641d9de460029d19e5","tid":2517253,"uid":53498,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"無視佢係最好方法"},{"pid":"aa6a01b58793bacd022e98aa298415d50a65a854","tid":2517253,"uid":9747,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"06e7cdbde785607c11e06d641d9de460029d19e5","tid":2517253,"uid":53498,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"無視佢係最好方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:18:04.000Z","msg":"report好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db1c7607b16a5613fec97ec18759097cc48c132","tid":2517253,"uid":377811,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"得啦成個連登都係傻㗎嘛<br />\n得佢一個咁醒咪由佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab93a40ffaeac052c77a733f05ad8234d70dc198","tid":2517253,"uid":241742,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"熱狗傻閪衛星page"},{"pid":"793ec713fb6714be8ef360cd219ee991718b5f24","tid":2517253,"uid":160592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"大把啦呢度"},{"pid":"3a593a2551a3b6fceb358ee16acf72554f7d6a35","tid":2517253,"uid":1249,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:58:31.000Z","msg":"連登大把熱狗屌人戴口罩"},{"pid":"dad690487905cde8f6b40e2c1d865edf206f626e","tid":2517253,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚知呢d撚樣乜撚野心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e79b3c00d16fcff1992813822452586768162d","tid":2517253,"uid":226622,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"淨係講一樣野, 成日單單打打咩「尻戴口罩」, 佢